data.description: Welcome to your place in heaven! Peace, serenity and beautiful views is what this home and community have to offer you! This is Arizona living at its finest in the Active Adult lake Inspired community of CantaMia. You will feel right at home in this 3 bedroom, 2 bath, plus office nicely upgraded Maestro floorplan. The large open kitchen offers quartz counters, maple cabinets, subway tiled backsplash, wall oven/microwave, gas cooktop with hood and huge walk-in pantry. Your guests will enjoy the extended outdoor patio area when you open the large glass slider to extend the entertainment area of the home. The master bedroom en suite is spacious and provides private access to the back patio. You will love the large walk-in tiled shower with bench, quartz counters and spacious walk-in closet! Garage offers built-in cabinet storage along with an instant hot water heater. Large backyard is landscaped and fully enclosed, providing privacy, but also offers views of the Estrella Mountains to the East. This home is less than two years old! Don't miss out! Schedule your showing to make this home yours today!
